# Syncthing ignore for briefing-v3 claude-4 to Mac mirror (send-only).
# 目标: Mac 拿到最小灾备集合 (code + DB + state), 排除大 / regenerable / host-local.

# host-specific
bin
/briefing

# git history: 代码已在 GitHub, .git 太大太频繁变
.git

# Go 下载缓存
vendor
node_modules

# SQLite WAL / SHM (毫秒级变动, 同步会撕裂 DB)
data/briefing.db-wal
data/briefing.db-shm

# 日志 / 运行锁
logs
*.pid
*.lock

# Claude / IDE 状态
.claude
.vscode
.idea
docs/chat

# 如不想把 secrets 同步到 Mac, 取消下一行注释:
# config/secrets.env
